title: More Talk with a Black Guy (Al Jackson)
itunes:title: More Talk with a Black Guy  with Al Jackson
description: Al Jackson came over to my apartment to talk about black people. But we got on a huge tangent that lasted an hour before we got on topic so I decided to let you guys hear it instead of throwing it out. Al is hilarious so I'm sure you'll enjoy it
